title: 1989 - U.S. Mint Set - 10 coin Uncirculated
description: 1989 U.S. Mint Set Single envelope set containing 10 uncirculated coins packaged by the U.S. Mint plus the P & D Medallion. Set includes a complete set of all 1989 coins issued from the Philadelphia Mint ("P" mint mark) and Denver Mint ("D" mint mark). The Quality of the coins in the mint sets are higher than coins put out for circulation. Comes in original government packaging*, as shown, with Certificates of Authenticity**. *While we do our best to handpick the nicest quality packaging due to the nature and age of mint sets being in envelopes we cannot guarantee the condition of the outer envelope, only the condition of the coins.** Packaging and CoA will vary by year.
